2018-02-03  Ben Collver <bencollver@gmail.com>

	* helpdeco.c: topic count by bytes / sizeof(int32_t) not
	sizeof(long).  this is why if you typecast bytes to struct you use stdint.h not
	assume sizeof(long) == 4.  Pulled from:

	https://github.com/joncampbell123/helpdeco/commit/65dfecb19ddc9664117b1b418db9981fbc148731

